cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper is about image completion using generative adversarial networks (GANs) and perceptual networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of different losses and the design of a lightweight generator architecture, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the analysis of complex structures and semantical similarity, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
